                    CA CCSS: {std}
                  </span>
                ))}
              </div>

              <button className="mt-6 w-full py-2 bg-slate-50 border border-slate-200 rounded-lg text-slate-600 text-sm font-bold hover:bg-indigo-50 hover:border-indigo-200 hover:text-indigo-600 transition-all">
